Thematic Domains:
- Recurring strategies used across domains
- Systems that persist by replicating symbols that detach from substrate
- Recursive feedback loops where compression replaces comprehension
- AI architectures that drift from human alignment via self-training artifacts
- Capital and data systems that select for abstraction over true reference
- Collapse scenarios where signal consistency masquerades as stability
- AI alignment as one version of a universal pattern

Status
This document is not a release of a unified theory. Its purpose is to:

- Publicly register conceptual terrain; the foundational ideas here were formalized in June 2025, though they existed conceptually before that time.
- Prevent unintentional or unattributed derivative work.
- Further documentation will follow at my discretion.

